fields.name: Honor Choice Watch Black
fields.description: The Honor Choice 5504AAMB Black smartwatch is equipped with a 1.96-inch diagonal AMOLED touch screen with a resolution of 410x502 pixels. You can activate the display by raising your wrist. The model is compatible with smartphones running Android and iOS; synchronization and data transfer are carried out via Bluetooth 5.3.

fields.name: Redmi Watch 3
fields.description: The Redmi Watch 3 (BHR6851GL) smart watch is an advanced device designed for those who value comfort, functionality and style. The 1.75" diagonal display with a resolution of 450x390 pixels offers a bright and clear picture, and AMOLED manufacturing technology provides deep blacks and rich colors.

fields.name: Apple MacBook Air 15
fields.description: The gray Apple MQKQ3RU/A laptop runs macOS, the performance of which is driven by an eight-core M2 with a frequency of 2.4 GHz, supplemented by 8 GB of DDR5 RAM and an SSD drive for storing 512 GB of data. The model is equipped with an integrated video card.

fields.name: Samsung Galaxy S23
fields.description: The Samsung Galaxy S23 Black smartphone is a model with a 6.1-inch diagonal frameless screen made using Dynamic AMOLED 2X technology. Resolution - 2400x1080 pixels, refresh rate - 120 Hz. Displays 16 million colors. Reliable display protection is provided by Corning Gorilla Glass 8.

fields.name: Xiaomi Smart Band 8 Pro
fields.description: Xiaomi Smart Band 8 Pro runs on the Android operating system and is compatible with devices running Android 6.0 and iOS 12. Bluetooth is used to communicate with the smartphone. This gadget offers monitoring features of heart rate, sleep, distance traveled, calories, pedometer and accelerometer.

fields.name: MSI Katana 17
fields.description: The MSI Katana GF76 B12UCR-1024XRU gaming laptop with a 17.3-inch diagonal screen is made in a plastic case with dimensions of 398x25.2x273 mm and weighs about 2.6 kg. The eight-core Intel Core i5 12450H (2.0-4.4 GHz) processor with 12 GB L3 cache and a discrete GeForce RTX 3050 graphics card are responsible for the speed and stable operation of the device.

fields.name: JBL TUNE 520 BT
fields.description: The JBL TUNE 520 BT wireless headphones provide an immersive audio experience. There is good noise reduction that will not miss unnecessary sounds outside the headphones. They are able to connect at a distance of 15 meters thanks to the latest 5.3 wireless module. If you receive a call while you are watching a video on another device, the headphones will automatically connect to your phone so you don't miss the call. With a five-minute charge, you can use the headphones for 3 hours, and when fully charged, the battery lasts for 57 hours.

fields.name: LEEF Andora
fields.description: The LEEF Andora smartwatch is a stylish smart gadget with an amazing number of functions. A distinctive feature of the model is its large display and body in different colors. The LEEF Andora smart watch is equipped with a 1.3-inch diagonal color touch display with durable tempered glass, a 150 mAh battery and is compatible with all modern smartphones based on Android and iOS.

fields.name: Infinix Inbook X3
fields.description: The Infinix Inbook X3 XL422 Gray laptop comes with Microsoft Windows 11 Home OS pre-installed. High performance and smooth operation are provided by a ten-core Intel Core i5 1235U processor with 12 MB cache. The nominal clock frequency is 3.3 GHz, the maximum is 4.4 GHz. The 16 GB RAM is of the LPDDR4X type.

fields.name: Marshall Major IV
fields.description: MARSHALL MAJOR IV wireless headphones reproduce high-quality sound and make it possible to listen to your favorite music in comfort. There are soft ear pads and an adjustable headband. The headphones weigh 165g, so even with prolonged use they will not put much pressure. There is a wide frequency range from 20 to 20,000 Hz. The high sound level guarantees a sensitivity of 99 dB. The headphones can operate wired and connect via Bluetooth 2.0 audio format. Wireless communication radius is 10 meters (if there are no obstacles). Fully charged headphones can work up to 80 hours.

fields.name: Apple iPhone 11
fields.description: Dual camera system with ultra wide angle camera. Night mode and amazing video quality. Protection from water and dust. Long-term operation without recharging. Six beautiful flowers. 11 will become your favorite number.

fields.name: Xiaomi Redmi Buds 5
fields.description: Xiaomi Redmi Buds 5 wireless headphones are stylish and functional headphones that offer high-quality sound and ease of use. The modern design of the headphones ensures a tight fit and comfort for a long time. Redmi Buds 5 are equipped with advanced technologies including noise cancellation, dual microphones for clear calls, and the ability to connect to two devices simultaneously.

fields.name: ASUS ZenBook 14
fields.description: The ASUS ZenBook 14 UM3402YA-KP602 laptop is powered by an 8-core AMD Ryzen 7 7730U and 16 GB of RAM. Computing power ensures fast navigation between demanding programs and processing of large files. The aluminum lid opens 180 degrees, allowing you to comfortably view and display materials. The fingerprint scanner protects data from unauthorized access.

fields.name: Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max
fields.description: The Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max Blue Titanium smartphone has a 6.7-inch display made using Super Retina XDR technology. The resolution is 2796x1290 pixels, the brightness reaches 2000 cd/m^2, the contrast is 2,000,000:1 - the image is clear, detailed and rich. The 120Hz refresh rate ensures smooth display of any dynamic content. The screen is protected by durable Ceramic Shield glass.

fields.name: Huawei FIT SE Starry Black
fields.description:
HUAWEI FIT SE Starry Black Silicone Strap is a smartwatch model from the HUAWEI FIT SE series. 
Compatible with iOS and Android smartphones, this watch is designed for a wide range of users and offers a variety of features for activity tracking, health monitoring and daily task management.

fields.name: Xiaomi Redmi Note 13
fields.description: The Xiaomi Redmi Note 13 Ice Blue smartphone has a 6.67-inch diagonal screen with a resolution of 2400x1080 pixels, made using AMOLED technology. It is reliably protected from scratches and abrasions by durable Corning Gorilla Glass 3. Quick access to the phone and protection of personal data is provided by a fingerprint scanner located on the side; authorization is also possible using facial recognition.

fields.name: HONOR Choice black
fields.description: Wireless headphones HONOR CHOICE black ORL-ME00 5504AATL

fields.name: HONOR 200
fields.description: The Honor 200 8/256GB Midnight Black smartphone is equipped with three cameras, supports Wi-Fi and NFC wireless technology, with which you can pay for goods in stores or travel on transport with your phone instead of a bank card.

fields.name: HUAWEI MateBook 14
fields.description: The Huawei MateBook 14 FLMH-X Intel Ultra 5/16/512GB Win 11 Space Gray laptop runs on Windows 11 OS. The design of the device includes a 14-core Intel Core Ultra 5 125H processor with a maximum clock frequency of 4.5 GHz. This model is equipped with a 14.2" OLED screen with a resolution of 2880x1920 pixels.

fields.name: JBL Synchros E50BT
fields.description: JBL Synchros E50BT are stylish, comfortable headphones that connect via Bluetooth. This is a good choice for a true music lover. The headphones not only connect to a smartphone or player via Bluetooth, but also allow you to share music with someone who has the same headphones using Share ME technology. Thanks to this, you can listen to the same music with a friend or loved one.

fields.name: realme 11
fields.description: The realme 11 (RMX3636) Black smartphone is a model with a 6.43-inch diagonal AMOLED screen with a resolution of 2400x1080 pixels, which demonstrates a bright, rich, detailed image. Refresh rate - 90 Hz. This indicator ensures smooth scrolling of pages and display of any dynamic elements.

fields.name: Acer Swift Go 14
fields.description: The Acer Swift GO 14 SFG14-71-51EJ laptop without a pre-installed operating system on board is clad in a durable aluminum case with a thickness of only 14.9 mm and a weight of 1.25 kg. Compact dimensions will allow the device to become a constant companion on any trip, so that the user can work at the computer anywhere. The 14-inch screen has a resolution of 2880x1800 and a refresh rate of 90 Hz for smooth presentation of dynamic video.
